Demonstrating various escapings.

<% local text = '<a>a_link:to_a_link</a>' %>

No escaping:
<%= text %>


<%!escape latex %>
LaTeX escaping:
<%= text %>

<%!escape url %>
URL escaping:
<%= text %>

<%!escape html %>
HTML escaping:
<%= text %>

<%!escape none %>
No escaping again:
<%= text %>

one time LaTeX escaping:
<%=latex text %>

one time URL escaping:
<%=url text %>

one time HTML escaping:
<%=html text %>

No escaping again:
<%!escape html %>
<%=none text %>

